Upper Case
---------------------------------
1. select text
2. ctrl + shift + x

Lower Case 
---------------------------------
1. select text
2. ctrl + shift + y

System.out.println('')
---------------------------------
1. write "system"   
2. ctrl + space

main()
---------------------------------
1. write "main"
2. ctrl + space

for loop
---------------------------------
1. write "for"
2. ctrl + space
3. select "for -use index on array"

foreach loop
---------------------------------
1. write "foreach"
2. ctrl + space

while loop
---------------------------------
1. write "while"
2. ctrl + space
3. select "while loop with condition"

do ... while loop
---------------------------------
1. write "do"
2. ctrl + space
3. select "do - do while statement"

if___ else
---------------------------------
1. write "if"
2. ctrl + space
3. select "if - if statement"

selected code take up or down
---------------------------------
1. select code
2. alt + up  // take up
3. alt + down // take down

try{} catch {}
---------------------------------
1. select code
2. alt + shift + z
3. select "try/catch block"

setter and getter generate to access private variable of class
--------------------------------------------------------------
1. write variable as "private String name;"
2. alt + shift + s, r
3. or right click --> Source --> Generate Getter and Setter

create Constructor of Class
---------------------------------
right click --> Source --> Generate constructor using fields

Formatting Code in proper alignment
---------------------------------
ctrl + shift + f

import package
---------------------------------
ctrl + shift + o

Commenting
---------------------------------
1. select code 
2. ctrl + /      //comment in/out
3. ctrl + shift + /   //multi line comment

Rename variable
---------------------------------
1. select variable
2. alt + shift + R
3. rename it

Go particular line in code
---------------------------------
ctrl + L

Find particular method
---------------------------------
ctrl + o

Make a new method by extracting
---------------------------------
1. select code
2. alt + shift + m
3. give "Method Name" --> ok





